  ::= { bcsTrapElements 16 }


  trapChangedValueOID       OBJECT-TYPE
       SYNTAX          DisplayString
       MAX-ACCESS      read-only
       STATUS          current
       DESCRIPTION 
        "This OBJECT IDENTIFIER is used to hold specific information about 
