  ::= { bcsTrapElements 17 }


  trapChangedValueIpAddress    OBJECT-TYPE
       SYNTAX          IpAddress
       MAX-ACCESS      read-only
       STATUS          current
       DESCRIPTION 
        "This OBJECT IDENTIFIER is used to hold specific information about 
