  ::= { bcsTrapElements 18 }

                       
  trapChangedValueInteger       OBJECT-TYPE
       SYNTAX          INTEGER (1..2147483647)
       MAX-ACCESS          read-only
       STATUS          current
       DESCRIPTION 
        "This 32 bit integer is used to hold specific information about 
